<% content_for :title, "Our Dog Walking Services | Walks & Wags Co." %>
<% content_for :meta_description, "Explore our dog walking services in East London. We offer both solo and group walks in Wanstead, Leyton, Woodford, Forest Gate, Hackney, and nearby areas. Tailored care for every pup." %>
<div class="services-container">
  <%= render 'shared/navbar' %>
  <section id="section3" class="color-bg" style="background-color: #E8AFC7;">
    <div class="prices-div">
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-center flex-column align-items-center">
        <h1 class="wanstead-wags-title titles prices text-center" style="color: #032B22;">Choose the Pawfect Service</h1>
        <p class="price-list text-center" style="font-family: Lato, serif, sans-serif !important;">  Choosing the right service for your dog can be tricky, but we’re here to help! Read the descriptions below to find the best option for your furry friend.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="services mt-0 gap-5">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center services-flex">
          <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center services-paragraph services-div">
            <h1 class="font-Abril text service services-description service-name">1-Hour Group Dog Walks ~ £17.50</h1>
            <p class="text service services-description services-font services-text">
              A fun and social experience for dogs who love companionship! Our group walks provide the perfect balance of exercise, enrichment, and socialisation.
            </p>
            <ul class="text service services-description services-font services-text">
              <li><strong>Small, Well-Matched Groups:</strong> Your dog will join a pack of 3-4 friendly, compatible dogs for an engaging and stimulating walk.</li>
              <li><strong>Exciting Outdoor Adventures:</strong> Walks take place in parks, fields, and woodlands, offering plenty of space to explore and play.</li>
              <li><strong>Physical & Mental Stimulation:</strong> Group walks encourage social interaction, improve confidence, and reinforce good manners.</li>
              <li><strong>Safe & Supervised:</strong> Our experienced dog walkers ensure a structured, enjoyable experience where every dog receives the attention they need.</li>
              <li><strong>Perfect for Social Dogs:</strong> Great for pups who thrive in a pack environment and enjoy making new friends on their daily adventures.</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="font-Abril text service services-description service-name">
              Two Dogs, One Household: £30 total (£15 per dog) — perfect for canine siblings!
            </p>
            <p class="text service services-description services-font services-text">
              Let your dog(s) experience the joy of group walks—an excellent way to keep them happy, healthy, and engaged!
            </p>
            <%= link_to("ENQUIRE NOW", new_contact_form_path, class: "mt-3 text-center button") %>
          </div>
            <div class="service-image-flex">
            <%= link_to new_contact_form_path do %>
              <%= image_tag "group_walks.png", loading:"lazy", alt: "Happy group of dogs walking together, ready to enjoy a fun and social adventure in parks, fields, and woodlands.", class: "service-page-images" %>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center services-flex">
          <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center services-paragraph services-div">
            <h1 class="font-Abril text services-description service service-name">1-Hour Solo Dog Walks ~ £25</h1>
            <p class="font-Abril services-description ">
              10% off when you book daily, Monday–Friday (can also include Saturday and Sunday)
            </p>
            <p class="text service services-description services-font services-text">
              A peaceful, one-on-one walking experience tailored to your dog's unique needs. These private walks allow them to explore at their own pace, free from distractions or stress.
            </p>
            <ul class="text service services-description services-font services-text">
              <li><strong>Gentle & Relaxing:</strong> A quiet, stress-free walk through woodlands, fields, or along tranquil lakes, perfect for calm exploration.</li>
              <li><strong>Ideal for Anxious or Nervous Dogs:</strong> Provides a comfortable and safe space for dogs who prefer solitude or struggle with social situations.</li>
              <li><strong>Perfect for Reactive Dogs:</strong> A controlled environment for dogs who may be reactive to others, ensuring a relaxed and enjoyable experience.</li>
              <li><strong>Tailored to Health Needs:</strong> Suitable for older dogs, those recovering from injury, or dogs needing a steady, low-impact walk.</li>
              <li><strong>Personalised Attention:</strong> Your dog gets dedicated care, with the walk adapted to their pace, interests, and personality.</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text services-description service services-font services-text">Whether your dog enjoys a slow stroll or a bit of adventure, our solo walks provide the perfect balance of exercise, enrichment, and relaxation.</p>
            <%= link_to("ENQUIRE NOW", new_contact_form_path, class: "mt-3 text-center button") %>
          </div>
          <div class="service-image-flex">
            <%= link_to new_contact_form_path do %>
              <%= image_tag "solo_walks.png", loading:"lazy", alt: "Golden Retriever standing upright, ready for a peaceful solo walk in nature—perfect for gentle exercise and mental stimulation.", class: "service-page-images" %>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center services-flex">
          <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center services-paragraph services-div">
            <h1 class="font-Abril text services-description service service-name">Overnight Dog Sitting ~ £40 per dog / 24 hours</h1>
            <p class="text service services-description services-font services-text">
              A cosy overnight care service so your dog feels safe, loved, and comfortable in their own home while you’re away. Perfect for holidays, evenings out, or weekends away.
            </p>
            <ul class="text service services-description services-font services-text">
              <li><strong>Familiar Environment:</strong> Dogs stay in the comfort of their own home to reduce stress and anxiety.</li>
              <li><strong>Daily Walks Included:</strong> Enrichment and exercise as part of the sitting service.</li>
              <li><strong>Peace of Mind:</strong> Updates and photos provided, so you know your pup is happy and settled.</li>
              <li><strong>Tailored to Routine:</strong> Feeding times, walk preferences, and bedtime habits followed as if you were there.</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text services-description service services-font services-text">
              Whether it’s one night or several, our overnight sitting service ensures your dog feels cared for, relaxed, and happy until you return.
            </p>
            <%= link_to("ENQUIRE NOW", new_contact_form_path, class: "mt-3 text-center button") %>
          </div>
          <div class="service-image-flex">
            <%= link_to new_contact_form_path do %>
              <%= image_tag "overnight-sitting.png", loading:"lazy", alt: "Happy group of dogs walking together, ready to enjoy a fun and social adventure in parks, fields, and woodlands.", class: "service-page-images" %>
            <% end %>
          </div>
